data.eml:eml: A new species of Anthonympha Moriuti (Lepidoptera: Plutellidae) from Russian Far East, with annotated check list of the genus

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ponomarenko, Margarita G. (2015): A new species of Anthonympha Moriuti (Lepidoptera: Plutellidae) from Russian Far East, with annotated check list of the genus. Zootaxa 4057 (3): 430-436, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4057.3.8
